'''雨帶'''指有明顯降雨的範圍，由[[雲|雲]]和[[降水|降水]]所結構。雨帶是由於溫度的差異而所產生的，而本身可以是層狀或對流。<ref>Glossary of Meteorology (2009). [http://amsglossary.allenpress.com/glossary/search?p=1&query=rainband&submit=Search Rainband.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606102457/http://amsglossary.allenpress.com/glossary/search?p=1&query=rainband&submit=Search |date=2011-06-06 }} Retrieved on 2008-12-24.</ref>從[[天氣雷達|天氣雷達]]圖像來看，這種降雨的範圍被看作為帶狀結構。<ref>Glossary of Meteorology (2009). [http://amsglossary.allenpress.com/glossary/search?id=banded-structure1 Banded structure.] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110606102630/http://amsglossary.allenpress.com/glossary/search?id=banded-structure1 |date=2011-06-06 }} Retrieved on 2008-12-24.</ref>[[熱帶氣旋|熱帶氣旋]]內的雨帶會呈彎曲狀，並包含了[[陣雨|陣雨]]和[[雷暴|雷暴]]；再加上[[眼壁|眼壁]]和[[風眼|風眼]]就構成了[[颶風|颶風]]或[[熱帶風暴|熱帶風暴]]，而雨帶的伸延範圍可以預計熱帶氣旋的強度。

